graph TD
    U[Users] --> CDN[Global CDN / Edge Network<br/>static assets, edge cache, WAF]

    CDN --> FE[Frontend - React SSR/ISR<br/>listing pages prerendered + revalidated,<br/>CSR for booking flow]
    subgraph Frontend Scaling
        FE
        FE2[Scaling: ISR + edge caching,<br/>stateless render nodes behind autoscaler,<br/>code-split bundles]
    end

    FE --> GW[API Gateway<br/>authN/authZ, rate limiting, routing, TLS]

    GW --> LS[Listings Service]
    GW --> SS[Search Service]
    GW --> BS[Booking Service]
    GW --> PS[Payments Service]
    GW --> RS[Reviews Service]
    GW --> MS[Media Service]

    subgraph Backend Scaling
        LS
        SS
        BS
        PS
        RS
        MS
        BE2[Scaling: independent horizontal autoscaling per service,<br/>async messaging via event bus - Kafka,<br/>circuit breakers + idempotent booking writes]
    end

    LS --> PG[(PostgreSQL<br/>sharded by listing/region,<br/>read replicas)]
    BS --> PG
    RS --> PG
    PS --> PG

    LS --> RD[(Redis<br/>hot listing cache, sessions,<br/>distributed locks for booking)]
    BS --> RD

    SS --> ES[(Elasticsearch<br/>full-text + geo search,<br/>ranking; fed by CDC pipeline)]
    PG -. change data capture .-> ES

    MS --> S3[(Object Storage - S3<br/>original photos)]
    S3 --> IMGCDN[Image CDN<br/>on-the-fly resizing, WebP/AVIF]
    IMGCDN --> CDN

    subgraph Storage Scaling
        PG
        RD
        S3
        ST2[Scaling: shard-per-region Postgres + replicas,<br/>Redis cluster with eviction tiers,<br/>S3 lifecycle tiers + CDN offload]
    end

    subgraph Search Scaling
        ES
        SE2[Scaling: index sharding + replicas,<br/>geo-partitioned indices,<br/>near-real-time CDC ingestion]
    end

    subgraph Deployment Scaling
        DEP[CI/CD: blue-green + canary releases,<br/>Kubernetes with HPA per service,<br/>multi-region active-active,<br/>observability: tracing, metrics, alerts]
    end
